| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5336 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ce98a20b-3aae-5741-8b55-57da8e75ab70"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
